OL,5, A senior nurse who took nearly 300 sick
OL,6, days due to severe migraines and       
OL,7, depression was wrongfully sacked, a    
OL,8, tribunal has found.                    
OL,10,FCaroline McKenzie was dismissed by     
OL,11,Fhospital bosses in Leicester following 
OL,12,Fnumerous warnings about her attendance.
OL,14,FHowever the tribunal heard both        
OL,15,Fmigraines and depression/anxiety are   
OL,16,Fconsidered as disabilities.            
OL,18,FA judge concluded she lost her job "at 
OL,19,Fleast partly" because of her           
OL,20,Fdisability-related absences.           
